                     <interp inst="t18161204-86-off458" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18161204-86-cd459" type="crimeDate">28th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18161204-86-off458 t18161204-86-cd459"></join>, one coal-scuttle, value 10s.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18161204-86-victim674" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     Hopkins
                  <interp inst="t18161204-86-victim674" type="surname" value="Hopkins"></interp>
